# Web3Forms — get a free access key at https://web3forms.com (enter the email
# where submissions should be delivered: darren@fugazycoding.com).
# This key is PUBLIC by design (it only routes mail to your address), so it is
# inlined into the static build via the NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key
